{"tid":741212,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[減肥撚]七月減肥日記","createTime":"2018-07-13T13:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T15:28:46.000Z","uid":46400,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"884bc8592fb1968c10d44b7c55da8c882a6bdf8a","tid":741212,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"開錯台重新再開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為完左個冬天春天一路係咁食搞到呢加個人圓曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以今日開始立志要減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標係希望8月之前可以有既彭于晏身型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我會set好曬program加日日做gym黎完成我既目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講少少身高體重先<br />\n身高:183cm<br />\n體重:84kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018-07-13<br />\n早餐:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/211203_8eba2ce54a79629562935cb6650f01a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F211203_8eba2ce54a79629562935cb6650f01a3.jpg&h=b7644d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nprotein曲奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/211225_a02dcd4d2183ae12b5be50c4b7c6d433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F211225_a02dcd4d2183ae12b5be50c4b7c6d433.jpg&h=c8f29042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋急凍pizza<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9eb671c8ddaba0d5077ae32cf1caf074c004ef","tid":741212,"uid":60404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:14:26.000Z","msg":"做咩啫你"},{"pid":"84013935ed5beacf876fccdcaacb9580622128ad","tid":741212,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"健身前餐:<br />\nPre-Workout 5g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n健身中餐:<br />\nBCAA支鏈氨基酸 5mg<br />\nCreatine 5g<br />\n<br />\n之後就係午餐:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/211551_dba0f95655d3a397c8d708179d85c994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F211551_dba0f95655d3a397c8d708179d85c994.jpg&h=b0c7f977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薯仔一個加西蘭花一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/211617_e10deb32bbb43b998117185b263e366c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F211617_e10deb32bbb43b998117185b263e366c.jpg&h=cffbf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋漢堡扒兩塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/211643_b5e314f765e149dd449a1f376ce96d6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F211643_b5e314f765e149dd449a1f376ce96d6a.jpg&h=0c28b837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過唔識整所以變左肉碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be44c524143b83fb40b40b8e5647a843bca977d","tid":741212,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f9eb671c8ddaba0d5077ae32cf1caf074c004ef","tid":741212,"uid":60404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-1