src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDumbbell Curls 6組6下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加 3組熱身15下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213129_3a75381a425661565b1de5578712e225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213129_3a75381a425661565b1de5578712e225.jpg&h=0e32c87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLying Tricep Press 6組6下 加 2組熱身12下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213151_e8c156bdf110c6d014ad41c4cf0c5e72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213151_e8c156bdf110c6d014ad41c4cf0c5e72.jpg&h=371802cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHammer Curls 5組10下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213221_b4607a5312942d1764c0ecbdd5aa3165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213221_b4607a5312942d1764c0ecbdd5aa3165.jpg&h=4882dcb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTriceps Pushdown 5組12下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213241_41a2d506441f879ddc9a4e87a9e69712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213241_41a2d506441f879ddc9a4e87a9e69712.jpg&h=116bc6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nConcentration Curls 4組12下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213304_dda8c668551cba229113bfd424ab03a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213304_dda8c668551cba229113bfd424ab03a0.jpg&h=4218af47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOne-Arm Dumbbell Triceps Extension 4組12下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213351_23104af9972cdf6faf79cc97ad8bcb61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213351_23104af9972cdf6faf79cc97ad8bcb61.jpg&h=b5437b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPalm up dumbbell wrist curls 4組20下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213412_b7769e73eb57907f89ad4dea9719b286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213412_b7769e73eb57907f89ad4dea9719b286.jpg&h=0e19fefd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩完手之後就玩腹了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHigh cable crunch 8組20下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213512_300865a059bc3e18e751e979a85170a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213512_300865a059bc3e18e751e979a85170a9.jpg&h=1065cd87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHigh cable woodchop 每邊4組20下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213803_dcfb460b824bb6de8511629ccc2c3aaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213803_dcfb460b824bb6de8511629ccc2c3aaa.jpg&h=cc03213f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHanging Leg Knee Raise 4組6下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為唔夠力了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/213808_886f3b5cce0c9364c48a660cdf8a65c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F213808_886f3b5cce0c9364c48a660cdf8a65c0.jpg&h=fe604468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df06d8f932edb8bb58b23c9272431669cb882bcb","tid":741212,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score"